2.5 物理设计
2.5.1表汇总
MySQL：

表4-1管理员表（root_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
loginname	varchar	20	主键	否	登录名
password	varchar	20		否	登录密码
username	varchar	20		否	用户名
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `root_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `root_inf`  (
  `loginname` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `username` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`loginname`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;

表4-2用户表（user_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
Id	int	11	主键	否	ID，自增
loginname	varchar	20		能	登录
password	varchar	20		否	登录密码
username	varchar	20		否	用户名
userphone	varchar	11		能	用户电话号码
userschool	varchar	10		能	用户毕业学校
userage	varchar	3		能	用户年龄
userinstruction	varchat	100		能	用户介绍
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `user_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `user_inf`  (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `loginname` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `password` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `username` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `userphone` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `userschool` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `userage` varchar(3) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `userinstruction` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT = 9 CHARACTER SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;	
表4-3职员表（employee_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
id	int	11	主键	否	数据ID，自增
dept-id	int	20	外键	能	部门id
job_id	int	15	外键	能	职位id
name	Varchar	20		能	姓名
card_id	integer	20		否	身份证号码
address	Varchar	50		否	地址
post_code	Varchar	20		能	邮政编码
tel	Varchar	20		能	固定电话
phone	Varchar	11		能	手机
salary	Varchar	10		能	工资
email	Varchar	50		能	邮箱
sex	int	11		能	性别
party	Varchar	10		能	生份
age	Varchar	3		能	年龄
race	Varchar	100		能	宗教
education	Varchar	10		能	学历
specially	Varchar	20		能	特点
hobby	Varchar	100		能	爱好
remark	Varchar	500		能	描述
DROP TABLE
IF
	EXISTS `employee_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `employee_inf` (
	`id` INT ( 11 ) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
	`dept_id` INT ( 11 ) NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`job_id` INT ( 11 ) NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`name` VARCHAR ( 20 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`card_id` VARCHAR ( 20 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`address` VARCHAR ( 50 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`post_code` VARCHAR ( 50 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`tel` VARCHAR ( 20 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`phone` VARCHAR ( 11 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`salary` VARCHAR ( 10 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`email` VARCHAR ( 50 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`sex` INT ( 11 ) NOT NULL,
	`party` VARCHAR ( 10 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`age` VARCHAR ( 3 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`race` VARCHAR ( 100 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`education` VARCHAR ( 10 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`speciality` VARCHAR ( 20 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`hobby` VARCHAR ( 100 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`remark` VARCHAR ( 500 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY ( `id` ) USING BTREE 
) ENGINE = MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT = 7 CHARACTER 
SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;
表4-4部门表（dept_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
id	int	11	主键	否	id
name	varchar	50		否	名称
remark	varchar	300		否	标志
DROP TABLE
IF
	EXISTS `dept_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `dept_inf` (
	`id` INT ( 11 ) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
	`name` VARCHAR ( 50 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`remark` VARCHAR ( 300 ) CHARACTER 
	SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY ( `id` ) USING BTREE 
) ENGINE = MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT = 31 CHARACTER 
SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;-
表4-5职位表（job_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
id	int	11	主键	否	id
name	varchar	50		否	名称
remark	varchar	300		否	标志
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `job_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `job_inf`  (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `remark` varchar(300) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT = 13 CHARACTER SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;
表4-6招聘表（notice_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
id	int	11	主键	否	id
name	varchar	50		否	名称
remark	text			否	标志
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `notice_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `notice_inf`  (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `content` text CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT = 7 CHARACTER SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;
表4-1投递表（toudi_inf）
字段名称	类型	长度	主外键	能否为空	说明
noticeid	int	11		否	招聘id
userid	int	11		否	用户id


DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `toudi_inf`;
CREATE TABLE `toudi_inf`  (
  `noticeid` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `userid` int(11) NULL DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER SET = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;

